msgctxt "awcms.adminCopy.overviewDescription"
msgid "Welcome to the AWCMS-Micro demonstration plugin. This console allows you to manage audit logs, lifecycle events, and simulate Role-Based and Attribute-Based Access Control (RBAC/ABAC) policies securely without modifying the EmDash core."
msgstr "Selamat datang di plugin demonstrasi AWCMS-Micro. Konsol ini memungkinkan Anda mengelola log audit, event lifecycle, dan simulasi kebijakan Role-Based dan Attribute-Based Access Control (RBAC/ABAC) secara aman tanpa mengubah core EmDash."

